	<h4>Padding</h4>
	<p>Padding classes can define padding on all sides <code>.pad-*</code>, vertical padding <code>.pad-v-*</code>, horizontal padding <code>.pad-h-*</code>, or you can also specify top <code>.pad-top-*</code>, left <code>.pad-left-*</code>, bottom <code>.pad-bottom-*</code> and right <code>.pad-right-*</code>.</p>
	<p>The <code>*</code> will be replaced with whichever number from the spacing scale. For example, to have xxs padding on all sides of an object, you would add the class: <code>.pad-all-xxs</code>.
