<div class="page-section__sub-section">
	<h4>Margin</h4>
	<p>Margin classes follow the same pattern as padding. Margin classes can define margin on all sides <code>.margin-*</code>, vertical margin <code>.margin-v-*</code>, horizontal margin <code>.margin-h-*</code>, or you can also specify top <code>.margin-top-*</code>, left <code>.margin-left-*</code>, bottom <code>.margin-bottom-*</code> and right <code>.margin-right-*</code>.</p>
	<p>To have an lg margin on the left side of an object, you would add the class: <code>.margin-left-lg</code>.
